item.title: First_post
item.author: Thihan Moe Kyaw
item.description: Hi everyone! Welcome to my page! My name is Thihan Moe Kyaw. I am a current student at the University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign(UIUC). I am a master student at the Industrial & Enterprise Systems Engineering (ISE) and a graduate research assistant at the National Center for Supercomputing Applications(NCSA). You can learn more about me in the about me page. Thank you for visiting! Note: this is the new version of my website.
